text: Gheorghe Zamfirescu is a water polo player from Romania. Zamfirescu competed at the 1972 Summer Olympics and the 1976 Summer Olympics. He was born on 21 September 1946.Gheorghe Zamfirescu == References == Category:1946 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian water polo players Category:Olympians for Romania Category:Sportspeople from Bucharest
